#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&akregator; is a program to read <acronym>RSS</acronym> and other online "
"news feeds."
msgstr ""
"&akregator; on rakendus <acronym>RSS</acronym>- ja teiste võrgu-"
"uudistekanalite lugemiseks."

#. Tag: keyword
